  <section class="panel" style="margin-bottom:16px">
    <div class="panel-head"><div><p class="panel-title">本日対応が必要な案件</p><p class="panel-note">期限・配布中・再提案チャンスを先に確認します。</p></div><span class="badge ${todos.length?'red':'gray'}">${todos.length}件</span></div>
    <div class="panel-body" style="padding-top:8px">
      <div style="overflow-x:auto"><table class="table"><thead><tr><th style="width:86px">状態</th><th>案件</th><th>対応内容</th></tr></thead><tbody>${actionRows}</tbody></table></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="metrics">
    <div class="metric" onclick="go('deals')"><small>今月の新規案件</small><strong>${proposalsThisMonth}<em>件</em></strong><span>案件管理より（${tm.replace("-","/")}）</span></div>
    <div class="metric m2" onclick="go('deals')"><small>進行中案件</small><strong>${active}<em>件</em></strong><span>ヒアリング〜配布中</span></div>
    <div class="metric m3" onclick="go('responses')"><small>今月の配布部数</small><strong>${num(distThisMonth)}<em>部</em></strong><span>反響分析の実績記録より</span></div>
    <div class="metric m4" onclick="go('responses')"><small>累計平均反響率</small><strong>${totC?pct(Math.round(avgCvr*1000)/1000):"—"}</strong><span>反響 ${num(totR)}件 / 配布 ${num(totC)}部</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-31">
    <div class="stack">
      <section class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head"><div><p class="panel-title">配布部数と反響率の推移</p><p class="panel-note">直近6ヶ月。棒＝配布部数、線＝反響率(%)。</p></div>
          <button class="btn-sm" onclick="go('responses')">詳細分析へ</button></div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          ${totC?barChart(chartData):`<div class="empty"><strong>まだ実績データがありません</strong>反響分析で配布実績を記録すると、ここに推移が表示されます。<br><br><button class="btn-sm primary" onclick="go('responses')">実績を記録する</button>　<button class="btn-sm" onclick="seedDemo()">デモデータで試す</button></div>`}
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="panel">
